Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.50,0:00:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找吧  收集梦想的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无奈也能感受到此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表看起来更单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法坦诚表达心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.02,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把想说的话收藏在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.33,0:00:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今更不能说出幼稚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.70,0:00:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好说时间能解决一切 却怕无人能懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.21,0:00:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天24小时我都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.48,0:00:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.22,0:01:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是司空见惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.23,0:01:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是嘲笑着匆匆而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.37,0:01:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其执着回忆 不如寻找现在的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.13,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城主大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是黑巫女  椿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是前来阻挠咒术的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.39,0:02:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒老早就结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.62,0:02:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的  我是来接你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妖怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难伺候的老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们想借用一下那股力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪找我有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:02:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还很痛恨桔梗对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.91,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第60话 黑巫女 五十年的诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个你念念看  日暮同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前学过的也忘光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像愈来愈被抛在后面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇没什么精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那个  旧男友的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个明明劈腿甩掉戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爱吃醋的暴力任性男人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是还牵扯不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神嘛  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点忘了他比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.18,0:04:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  那个臭男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然不想分手对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干脆点分了才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.00,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又发生什么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又和好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.57,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回到原点了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实他也有温柔的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.94,0:04:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.01,0:04:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很平常嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么这么沮丧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我最近一直请假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课业有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.88,0:04:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  因为戈薇常常请假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算每天上课也有可能跟不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要确实做好预习与复习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课就能很快乐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么怎么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不好的话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为步美一直很认真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.11,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是太晚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙又会跑来接我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还会来接你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是很体贴的男朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  他明明很爱吃醋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们又和好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇这样没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是致密的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了  老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.45,0:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落  我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑巫女  椿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.23,0:06:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我来到底有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约五十年前  你应该还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾和叫做桔梗的巫女战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺取四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的真清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑巫女  椿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邪恶的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意为我所用吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给你力量  我能得到什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.19,0:06:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给你四魂之玉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的手上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆变的妖怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意你的口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我本来的面貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个女人的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了永保青春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把魂魄出卖给妖怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对方还是不怎样的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人应该渴望更强的妖力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你说有四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用四魂之玉做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是永保青春吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.25,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落  你希望我做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给七宝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是犬夜叉喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.76,0:07:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别只顾着拿零嘴…拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的也该带一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.77,0:07:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多各式各样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御神酒和护身符也带去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不用了啦  爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你已经要出发了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人在等呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是犬夜叉哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想试着去战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你去了  因为你是胆小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会想回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.93,0:08:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太年纪还太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就不会怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概都已经习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧  姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就放着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有够久耶  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说太阳下山前就会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇好慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:09:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说太阳下山前就会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有感觉到什么吧  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有股奇怪的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个感觉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.51,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法师啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也发现了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.38,0:09:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…邪气悄悄的接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛在地面上爬一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.26,0:09:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?被咬了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  很慢耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道被什么东西咬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.54,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到那女人的血了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再带我过去一趟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很神气嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我碰到一个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该算是解决掉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没有被咬的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.87,0:12:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看那纸  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.77,0:12:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有带来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…式神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚是…四魂之玉碎片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.41,0:13:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片变黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.59,0:13:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片  进入了我的身体里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.47,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入那女人体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和充满奈落污秽的玉共鸣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而侵蚀那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.98,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是心灵还是身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.88,0:13:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人的命运就任我摆布了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.75,0:13:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿  别小看那个叫戈薇的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.46,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.86,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫戈薇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己中了诅咒都没发觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为桔梗的转世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个多厉害的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.87,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你想怎么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样直接咒杀她也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.77,0:14:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让犬夜叉的恶梦再次重现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那与心爱的女人相互残杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人怀念的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫姥姥  这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上之前的邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是某人在诅咒戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁敢诅咒戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.53,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是黑巫女的杰作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在井边咬伤戈薇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.44,0:14:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是黑巫女的使魔  式神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.51,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑巫女?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.28,0:14:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也知道她们的存在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.55,0:14:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专门接受诅咒委托的邪恶巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片受到污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是那家伙的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全进入戈薇的身体里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇或许会被碎片的毒毒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出黑巫女然后打倒她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要断绝诅咒非这样做不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留下来陪在戈薇身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较妥当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.84,0:15:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个方向可以感受到邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上来  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.70,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.71,0:15:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了犬夜叉  杀了犬夜叉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了犬夜叉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…别说了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还任性的抵抗着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了  椿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫戈薇的女人\N是巫女桔梗的转世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的手段是行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一个半妖男人夺去了心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵力也衰弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取那家伙守护的四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这原本是最好的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.81,0:16:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人竟然把我放的式神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原封不动的打回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚  我不想取你性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人故作清高的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.03,0:17:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来仍让我作呕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.52,0:17:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我去换个水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.77,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.87,0:17:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇还有救吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…可能戈薇本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.88,0:18:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在和诅咒战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇是很坚强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.59,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  再拖下去会承受不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还束手无策吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她垂死挣扎也差不多到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.87,0:18:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就实现你的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒他们还没\N抵达黑巫女的所在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇明明这么痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然只能旁观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  犬夜叉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是顽强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使身体被操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的心却还没丧失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这样更有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.46,0:20:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿  如果犬夜叉逃离那地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.20,0:20:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候就不用客气  咒杀戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.67,0:20:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.58,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇一定是被黑巫女操纵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪气愈来愈强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.47,0:20:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经和它战斗过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.85,0:21:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人我随时都能咒杀她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.76,0:21:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样让戈薇杀了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.36,0:21:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是逃走  让戈薇丧命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.08,0:21:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量痛苦吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.61,0:22:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.51,0:22:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.40,0:22:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了真正重要的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.91,0:22:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能舍弃其他一切就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.16,0:22:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而现实却是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.43,0:22:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的时刻只要随时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.23,0:22:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.07,0:23:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海浮现你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.61,0:23:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-但愿直到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.09,0:23:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远沉睡的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.46,0:23:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.93,0:23:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不止息存在我心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.89,0:23:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘在倒下之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.72,0:23:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经说她被什么咬了一口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.79,0:23:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能就是黑巫女的式神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.39,0:23:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.63,0:23:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快找到她的所在位置\N然后阻止她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.00,0:23:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然戈薇会将犬夜叉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.17,0:24:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个结界太强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光凭我的力量是不够的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.40,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.14,0:24:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.27,0:24:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.47,0:24:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.94,0:24:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现的桔梗与式神巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.44,0:24:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底五十年前发生了什么事


